        "description": "ch0246_lobby_5_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "このドレス、便利屋のみんなと選んだの。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_5_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_lobby_5_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "特別な思い出の服だからね、大切に着たいんだ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_5_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_login_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "いらっしゃい、先生！ドレス姿の可愛いムツキちゃんを待たせるなんて、",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_login_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_login_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "こっちこっち！今日は何して遊ぶ？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_login_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "あのね？こう見えても私、結構信頼してるんだよ？先生のこと。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_2_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "え、意外？……いつもイタズラばっかりしてるから？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_2_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_2_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "くふふっ。私だって誰彼構わずやるわけじゃないって。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_2_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_3_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "まあ、だから……そのお金をどうするかは、任せるよ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_3_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_3_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生なら、ちゃんと意味のあることに使ってくれるでしょ？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_3_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_3_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "どっかに寄付してもいいし、先生の活動資金にしてもいいし……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_3_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_4_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "それが嫌なら、先生が預かるってことにして――",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_4_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_4_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "私たちの未来のために取っておいても、いいかもね？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_5",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "え？何を言っているのかって？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_5.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_6",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "くふふっ！さあ？どういう意味だろうね♪",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_6.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_relationship_up_1",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生さぁ、自分がやってることの意味……ちゃんと分かってるの？くふふ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_relationship_up_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_relationship_up_2",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "あははっ！私も先生のこと、だーい好き！いろんな意味でね♪",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_relationship_up_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_relationship_up_3",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ふぅん……この感情の名前、私知ってる。気になるなら、教えてあげよっか？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_relationship_up_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_relationship_up_4",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "へ～？ふーん？そっかあ。先生は、も～っと私と仲良くなりたいんだね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_relationship_up_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_birthday_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "あははっ！お祝いしてくれてありがと、先生♪",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_birthday_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_birthday_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生が喜ぶかなって思ってドレスを着てみたんだけど……どう？嬉しい？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_birthday_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_birthday_player_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生、今日誕生日だよね？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_birthday_player_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_birthday_player_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "じゃあパーティーしよっ！パーティー♪",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_birthday_player_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_halloween_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "私のドレスが赤い理由……なんでか分かる？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_halloween_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_halloween_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "血がついても目立たないから――",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_halloween_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_halloween_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "なーんて！あははっ！騙された～？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_halloween_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_newyear_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生、あけおめ～今年も楽しい一年になるといいね♪",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_newyear_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_newyear_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生もそう思うでしょ？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_newyear_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_xmas_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "クリスマスにドレスを着るのって、何か特別な意味があるのかな？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_xmas_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0246_season_xmas_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "一緒に調べてみない？くふふっ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_xmas_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "CH0246_Title",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ブルーアーカイブ！くふふっ！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/CH0246_Title.ogg"
